{"id":30075,"type":4,"name":"The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-Earth II","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/cd/0e/30075_3b3t9.jpg","rating":{"total":16,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":4,"6":6,"7":4,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.3},"summary":"　　《魔戒：中土之战2》新加入的J.R.R.托尔金原着小说内容，让游戏展现前所未见的深度，并展开启金奖电影三部曲范畴之外的全新战役。在北方开辟战场，并且指挥中土世界历史上的最着名种族：精灵和矮人军队，或是与率领从未在‘魔戒’电影里出现的英雄和生物与邪恶阵营并肩作战。玩家可以创造/定制除了阿尔温这样的知名角色之外的自己的英雄，他们会随着游戏的进展越来越强大。作为新线影视的指环王电影基础上开发游戏的授权的补充，TolkienEnterprises授权EA在小说的基础上开发游戏。这样，《中土之战2》将把玩家带领到EA以前未涉及的小说世界中。有了来自J.R.RTolkien小说原作中的新内容，玩家可以对指环王进行前所未有的深入并且卷入到大受好评的电影三部曲中没有涉及的战役。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>指环王：中土战争2</li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/13930\">Electronic Arts</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/7590\">John Ronald Reuel Tolkien</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>魔戒之中土大战2</li><li><span>平台: </span>xbox360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Windows</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>RTS</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>Windows：2006/3/2；Xbox 360：2006/7/5</li>","collection":{"collect":21,"doing":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"RTS","count":6},{"name":"PC","count":2},{"name":"欧美系","count":2},{"name":"2006","count":1},{"name":"各种跳出","count":1}],"crt":[{"id":70117,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d2/49/70117_crt_nNtU2.jpg","name":"萨鲁曼","desc":"Christopher Lee"}],"staff":[{"id":13930,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ed/80/13930_prsn_10ahO.jpg","name":"艺电","desc":"发行"},{"id":7590,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/0b/e6/7590_prsn_XsS5i.jpg","name":"约翰·罗纳德·鲁埃尔·托尔金","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":113242,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c1/c1/113242_OyC9L.jpg","title":"The Lord of the Rings","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/113242"},{"id":235405,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/0a/06/235405_YzzOH.jpg","title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth","type":"前传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/235405"}],"like":[{"id":22954,"name":"战锤40000：星际战士","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/73/94/22954_e0ygb.jpg"},{"id":4446